323
00:16:07,440 --> 00:16:08,440
It's enough, Dad.

324
00:16:11,000 --> 00:16:12,030
You replied in unison.

325
00:16:12,360 --> 00:16:13,720
Dad, it's mainly because

326
00:16:13,777 --> 00:16:15,288
those who are capable work harder.

327
00:16:15,355 --> 00:16:16,155
Eat more.

328
00:16:17,266 --> 00:16:18,733
Being able to eat is a blessing.

329
00:16:22,600 --> 00:16:23,000
Delicious.

330
00:16:25,711 --> 00:16:26,666
Speaking of, Dad.

331
00:16:27,622 --> 00:16:28,511
I don't think

332
00:16:28,600 --> 00:16:30,155
