333
00:16:30,222 --> 00:16:31,870
I'm going to check the plane tickets

334
00:16:31,955 --> 00:16:33,555
to go back to the United States.

335
00:16:34,755 --> 00:16:36,030
You're going back so soon?

336
00:16:38,519 --> 00:16:39,000
No.

337
00:16:40,000 --> 00:16:41,559
Your wound hasn't healed yet.

338
00:16:42,440 --> 00:16:44,080
It's a long flight.

339
00:16:44,080 --> 00:16:45,688
You'll be on the plane for so long.

340
00:16:45,688 --> 00:16:47,200
If your wound is exposed again...

341
00:16:47,480 --> 00:16:47,960
Besides,

342
00:16:48,559 --> 00:16:50,559
