after you return?

343
00:16:51,360 --> 00:16:52,679
Is the food abroad

344
00:16:52,679 --> 00:16:53,720
nutritious?

345
00:16:54,244 --> 00:16:55,600
It's better to stay at home.

346
00:16:55,670 --> 00:16:56,600
Rest a bit longer.

347
00:16:59,519 --> 00:17:00,720
No, Dad.

348
00:17:00,879 --> 00:17:01,960
Stop eating for a while.

349
00:17:02,080 --> 00:17:03,639
Here, let me ask you a question.

350
00:17:03,639 --> 00:17:04,640
Answer me honestly.

351
00:17:06,533 --> 00:17:07,880
Are you reluctant to let me go?

352
00:17:11,480 --> 00:17:12,119
Yes.

353
00:17:13,839 --> 00:17:16,720
You've learned to express your feelings.

354
00:17:17,000 --> 00:17:17,720
There's progress.

355
00:17:18,200 --> 00:17:19,880
You have to go even if he's reluctant.

356
00:17:20,039 --> 00:17:21,200
You're a hindrance here.

357
00:17:21,559 --> 00:17:22,880
Shut up.

358
00:17:23,200 --> 00:17:24,920
Eat more sea cucumber porridge.

359
00:17:24,920 --> 00:17:26,060
Let me pour you another bowl.

360
00:17:26,066 --> 00:17:26,800
Give it to Dad.

361
00:17:27,200 --> 00:17:27,400
Yes.

362
00:17:27,400 --> 00:17:28,777
Those who are capable work harder.

363
00:17:28,790 --> 00:17:29,711
Dad, have another bowl.

364
00:17:31,160 --> 00:17:32,960
(Sleepwear)

365
00:17:39,400 --> 00:17:40,000
You're back?

366
00:17:43,160 --> 00:17:44,519
Why do you reek of alcohol?

367
00:17:44,600 --> 00:17:45,622
Here, give it to me.

368
00:17:46,960 --> 00:17:47,839
I drank at noon.

369
00:17:47,839 --> 00:17:49,799
I've rested in the company
the entire afternoon.

370
00:17:50,600 --> 00:17:51,960
I really can't drink this much.

371
00:17:52,000 --> 00:17:53,088
It's really a waste of time.

372
00:17:53,160 --> 00:17:54,079
Take a shower first.

373
00:17:55,244 --> 00:17:55,955
Take a shower.

374
00:18:02,359 --> 00:18:04,559
Dear, do you want me to help you?

375
00:18:04,559 --> 00:18:05,680
I'll help you rub your back.

376
00:18:06,079 --> 00:18:06,880
What are you doing?

377
00:18:07,759 --> 00:18:09,640
- I'm afraid you'll fall.
- I'm taking a shower.

378
00:18:10,000 --> 00:18:11,519
Aren't you drunk?

379
00:18:11,800 --> 00:18:12,790
Let me help you wash.

380
00:18:12,880 --> 00:18:14,666
You make me sound like a three-year-old.

381
00:18:15,160 --> 00:18:15,799
Get out.

382
00:18:16,559 --> 00:18:17,920
Okay, wash yourself.

383
00:18:20,160 --> 00:18:21,000
Close the door.

384
00:18:26,000 --> 00:18:27,319
Here, have a glass of honey water.

385
00:18:28,119 --> 00:18:29,400
Sober up.

386
00:18:29,759 --> 00:18:30,279
Miss.

387
00:18:30,279 --> 00:18:32,200
You've ruined the warmth
in the bathroom.

388
00:18:32,359 --> 00:18:33,749
Who are you calling Miss?

389
00:18:33,750 --> 00:18:35,400
Drink it now.
Are you drinking it or not?

390
00:18:35,444 --> 00:18:36,079
I'll drink it.

391
00:18:36,080 --> 00:18:37,000
Hurry up and get out.

392
00:18:38,079 --> 00:18:38,799
It won't kill you.

393
00:18:42,039 --> 00:18:42,359
You...

394
00:18:42,711 --> 00:18:44,422
You didn't close the door again.

395
00:18:46,160 --> 00:18:47,839
Mature women are treasures.

396
00:18:47,839 --> 00:18:49,240
There are new surprises every day.

397
00:18:49,800 --> 00:18:51,310
What do you think of this sleepwear?

398
00:18:52,079 --> 00:18:53,599
My wife looks beautiful in anything.

399
00:18:53,955 --> 00:18:55,222
It's not me who wears it.

400
00:18:55,400 --> 00:18:57,920
Ms. Lian bought this sleepwear.

401
00:18:59,488 --> 00:19:00,400
She's exposing here

402
00:19:01,759 --> 00:19:02,599
and here.

403
00:19:03,022 --> 00:19:04,880
Who do you think she's wearing this for?

404
00:19:05,240 --> 00:19:06,920
Your dad is already 70 years old.

405
00:19:09,799 --> 00:19:11,279
You'll also buy one when I'm 70.

406
00:19:13,400 --> 00:19:16,200
Your dad and Ms. Lian
are the embodiment of love.

407
00:19:18,400 --> 00:19:19,920
Do you hear me?

408
00:19:20,044 --> 00:19:21,920
I can't make a mistake
on even a decimal point.

409
00:19:21,955 --> 00:19:23,977
You can't make a mistake
on even a decimal point?

410
00:19:24,022 --> 00:19:26,266
(Financial Statement)
You can ignore your wife then?

411
00:19:26,599 --> 00:19:28,269
Every day, you either drink or work

412
00:19:28,270 --> 00:19:30,266
and sit in front of the computer
when you get home.

413
00:19:30,266 --> 00:19:31,720
You don't care about me at all.

414
00:19:31,830 --> 00:19:33,644
How do you want me to care about you?

415
00:19:35,200 --> 00:19:35,960
I drank.

416
00:19:36,240 --> 00:19:37,160
I drank today.

417
00:19:37,440 --> 00:19:38,480
You said it last time.

418
00:19:38,480 --> 00:19:40,800
Drinking and indulging in sex
are harmful to my health.

419
00:19:41,160 --> 00:19:41,880
Hug me then.

420
00:19:42,777 --> 00:19:44,160
It shouldn't be hard to hug me.

421
00:19:44,559 --> 00:19:45,960
This report is urgent.

422
00:19:45,960 --> 00:19:46,680
I told you.

423
00:19:46,720 --> 00:19:47,319
Hug me.

424
00:19:47,319 --> 00:19:48,279
Just one minute.

425
00:20:05,599 --> 00:20:06,279
Shen Qing.

426
00:20:06,422 --> 00:20:08,511
How long has it been
since we last hugged each other?

427
00:20:12,333 --> 00:20:13,350
You have 30 seconds left.

428
00:20:14,920 --> 00:20:17,066
Do you think hugging your wife
is like doing a plank?

429
00:20:17,160 --> 00:20:18,000
Is it unbearable

430
00:20:18,000 --> 00:20:19,279
that you even have to count down?

431
00:20:19,311 --> 00:20:20,679
I think you're overly unromantic.

432
00:20:20,680 --> 00:20:21,510
You need to fix that.

433
00:20:21,511 --> 00:20:22,600
Fix it however you want.

434
00:20:22,711 --> 00:20:23,577
One minute is up.

435
00:20:23,920 --> 00:20:25,319
Shen Qing.

436
00:20:26,279 --> 00:20:27,359
I'm talking to you seriously.

437
00:20:27,680 --> 00:20:28,440
Starting tomorrow,

438
00:20:28,644 --> 00:20:30,133
you have to learn from your dad.

439
00:20:30,133 --> 00:20:32,030
You must hug me
before going to bed at night

440
00:20:32,030 --> 00:20:33,890
and kiss me goodbye
when leaving in the morning

441
00:20:33,955 --> 00:20:35,711
There are no specific rules
during the day.

442
00:20:35,839 --> 00:20:36,400
But you

443
00:20:36,590 --> 00:20:38,444
have to send me
a WeChat message at noon.

444
00:20:39,519 --> 00:20:41,440
Liu Lina, what triggered you?

445
00:20:43,079 --> 00:20:44,319
When you reach middle age,

446
00:20:44,839 --> 00:20:46,920
you need a sense of ritual in life
all the more.

447
00:20:49,160 --> 00:20:51,480
What kind of idol drama
have you been watching?

448
00:21:08,160 --> 00:21:08,519
Dai.

449
00:21:12,319 --> 00:21:13,160
This is for you.

450
00:21:14,000 --> 00:21:15,680
Life needs a sense of ritual after all.

451
00:21:15,755 --> 00:21:17,830
I remember
that these are your favorite flowers.

452
00:21:28,640 --> 00:21:29,079
Dai.

453
00:21:31,240 --> 00:21:31,680
Dai.

454
00:21:32,799 --> 00:21:33,480
I think

455
00:21:33,960 --> 00:21:35,240
some things should be made clear.

456
00:21:37,920 --> 00:21:39,119
I received a call

457
00:21:40,044 --> 00:21:41,270
at the operating room door.

458
00:21:42,400 --> 00:21:43,200
The school called.

459
00:21:44,519 --> 00:21:47,039
They said my son
was beaten by his senior.

460
00:21:47,266 --> 00:21:48,644
He was seriously injured.

461
00:21:49,400 --> 00:21:50,200
That's why I...

462
00:21:50,640 --> 00:21:51,160
Liang.

463
00:21:55,000 --> 00:21:56,319
Let me come clean.

464
00:22:02,759 --> 00:22:03,960
My illness this time

465
00:22:06,160 --> 00:22:07,640
cured all the after-effects

466
00:22:08,480 --> 00:22:09,279
from before.

467
00:22:19,079 --> 00:22:20,920
We had a serious relationship.

468
00:22:22,088 --> 00:22:23,350
I think that's good enough.

469
00:22:25,444 --> 00:22:26,400
Don't you think so?

470
00:22:32,240 --> 00:22:33,200
I've moved on.

471
00:22:34,559 --> 00:22:35,599
I hope you can move on too.

472
00:22:47,155 --> 00:22:48,355
A toast to the present.

473
00:23:26,720 --> 00:23:30,920
(Tomb of Loving Mother, Chen Jingmin)

474
00:23:30,920 --> 00:23:31,279
Mom.

475
00:23:32,066 --> 00:23:34,266
I will be returning
to the United States tomorrow.

476
00:23:36,240 --> 00:23:37,960
The next time I come back

477
00:23:38,977 --> 00:23:40,866
will probably be
during the Qingming Festival.

478
00:23:41,720 --> 00:23:43,680
I never came back
during the Chinese New Year.

479
00:23:45,088 --> 00:23:47,266
Now, I come back every year
for the Qingming Festival.

480
00:23:49,519 --> 00:23:50,599
How unfilial am I?

481
00:23:56,359 --> 00:23:56,799
Mom.

482
00:23:58,480 --> 00:23:59,759
I still miss you very much.

483
00:24:02,079 --> 00:24:03,079
I really miss you.

484
00:24:05,279 --> 00:24:06,160
And why do you

485
00:24:06,160 --> 00:24:08,160
keep appearing in Shen Duole's dreams?

486
00:24:08,160 --> 00:24:09,519
Why don't you appear in my dreams?

487
00:24:09,960 --> 00:24:11,160
My last name is Shen too.

488
00:24:11,599 --> 00:24:13,240
And didn't you say before

489
00:24:13,355 --> 00:24:15,733
that I will always
be your and Dad's little princess?

490
00:24:15,777 --> 00:24:16,444
Alright.

491
00:24:16,466 --> 00:24:18,177
Mom doesn't want to see you cry.

492
00:24:22,155 --> 00:24:23,111
Speaking of, Mom.

493
00:24:23,319 --> 00:24:25,160
I visited Dad this time.

494
00:24:25,799 --> 00:24:27,920
He's doing well in every aspect.

495
00:24:29,319 --> 00:24:29,680
Well...

496
00:24:30,599 --> 00:24:31,960
Ms. Lian is pretty good too.

497
00:24:32,079 --> 00:24:33,200
Why are you telling Mom this?

498
00:24:33,844 --> 00:24:34,890
It's almost time to leave.

499
00:24:35,039 --> 00:24:36,200
Mom, we'll go now.

500
00:24:36,640 --> 00:24:37,759
I'll stop talking.

501
00:24:38,519 --> 00:24:39,640
Mom, we'll go now.

502
00:24:39,640 --> 00:24:40,911
