503
00:24:46,400 --> 00:24:46,720
Qing.

504
00:24:47,319 --> 00:24:47,920
Sorry.

505
00:24:48,400 --> 00:24:50,400
I'm still so willful at this age.

506
00:24:50,759 --> 00:24:51,640
I was even mad at you.

507
00:24:52,039 --> 00:24:53,079
We're a family.

508
00:24:53,079 --> 00:24:54,960
There aren't
that many things to apologize for.

509
00:24:56,133 --> 00:24:58,310
We're all geniuses
when it comes to expressing hatred.

510
00:24:59,000 --> 00:25:01,640
But we only say one thing
when it comes to expressing love.

511
00:25:02,160 --> 00:25:03,519
We're a family.

512
00:25:04,559 --> 00:25:06,200
Alright, stop being sentimental.

513
00:26:27,440 --> 00:26:28,640
Did I forget to tell you?

514
00:26:30,799 --> 00:26:31,880
Have you added ginger?

515
00:26:32,400 --> 00:26:33,680
Dai doesn't like ginger.

516
00:26:36,039 --> 00:26:37,359
I asked before.

517
00:26:37,680 --> 00:26:38,319
Don't worry.

518
00:26:38,599 --> 00:26:40,119
But I added a little ginger juice

519
00:26:40,720 --> 00:26:43,000
to remove the meat's raw smell.

520
00:26:43,880 --> 00:26:44,720
Good.

521
00:26:45,079 --> 00:26:45,640
Is that okay?

522
00:26:45,720 --> 00:26:46,079
Okay.

523
00:26:47,066 --> 00:26:48,711
Do you think this is about right?

524
00:26:50,960 --> 00:26:51,400
Good job.

525
00:26:54,039 --> 00:26:54,720
Look at this.

526
00:26:54,822 --> 00:26:55,920
It's pretty good, right?

527
00:26:57,039 --> 00:26:57,440
Not bad.

528
00:26:57,533 --> 00:26:58,266
It smells good.

529
00:26:58,711 --> 00:27:00,110
You seem to be quite good at it.

530
00:27:00,119 --> 00:27:00,599
Dad.

531
00:27:01,222 --> 00:27:02,955
Are you making me some egg dumplings?

532
00:27:02,960 --> 00:27:04,480
Yes, Ms. Lian said

533
00:27:04,933 --> 00:27:07,720
we should make your favorite
egg dumplings for the last meal.

534
00:27:08,755 --> 00:27:09,888
Have you packed your things?

535
00:27:09,911 --> 00:27:11,311
I'm almost done packing my luggage.

536
00:27:12,640 --> 00:27:13,039
Dad.

537
00:27:14,400 --> 00:27:15,640
After I leave,

538
00:27:16,444 --> 00:27:17,733
take good care of yourself.

539
00:27:18,119 --> 00:27:19,200
Most importantly,

540
00:27:20,088 --> 00:27:20,960
be nice to Ms. Lian.

541
00:27:24,866 --> 00:27:26,022
I'll keep that in mind.

542
00:27:26,800 --> 00:27:28,488
Then I'll give you
a few words of advice.

543
00:27:29,720 --> 00:27:30,680
After you go back,

544
00:27:31,000 --> 00:27:31,920
take care of yourself

545
00:27:32,519 --> 00:27:33,359
and eat on time.

546
00:27:34,200 --> 00:27:34,640
Also,

547
00:27:35,160 --> 00:27:36,799
consider moving home
as soon as possible.

548
00:27:37,319 --> 00:27:37,960
This home

549
00:27:38,480 --> 00:27:39,519
will always be yours.

550
00:27:39,920 --> 00:27:41,519
I know.

551
00:27:43,720 --> 00:27:44,279
Ms. Lian.

552
00:27:45,359 --> 00:27:47,720
The password to my room
is my dad's birthday.

553
00:27:48,200 --> 00:27:49,400
I think you already know that.

554
00:27:52,680 --> 00:27:53,440
If you find

555
00:27:54,200 --> 00:27:55,960
any of my mom's belongings,

556
00:27:56,319 --> 00:27:57,559
just put them in my room.

557
00:27:58,079 --> 00:27:58,480
Okay.

558
00:27:59,079 --> 00:27:59,400
Okay.

559
00:28:03,200 --> 00:28:03,640
Ms. Lian.

560
00:28:04,920 --> 00:28:07,279
Thank you again
for taking care of my dad.

561
00:28:09,519 --> 00:28:10,920
You gave my dad the courage to live

562
00:28:11,599 --> 00:28:12,680
and also made our home

563
00:28:13,444 --> 00:28:14,590
feel like a home again.

564
00:28:34,119 --> 00:28:34,559
Ms. Lian.

565
00:28:35,519 --> 00:28:36,319
I will now

566
00:28:37,359 --> 00:28:38,319
leave my dad to you.

567
00:28:43,359 --> 00:28:43,759
Okay.

568
00:28:55,377 --> 00:28:57,688
A mother worries about her son
when he's away from home.

569
00:29:00,200 --> 00:29:01,000
My daughter

570
00:29:02,066 --> 00:29:04,622
appears tough but is soft-hearted.
