710
00:33:21,270 --> 00:33:21,930
Let me help you.

711
00:33:22,200 --> 00:33:23,160
Here. Let me do it.

712
00:33:23,160 --> 00:33:23,799
No.

713
00:33:24,000 --> 00:33:24,960
I want to do it myself.

714
00:33:25,644 --> 00:33:26,480
By the way, Lina,

715
00:33:27,079 --> 00:33:29,039
