719
00:33:37,000 --> 00:33:37,960
Okay.

720
00:33:50,466 --> 00:33:51,200
What do you think?

721
00:33:51,933 --> 00:33:52,510
It tastes good.

722
00:33:55,640 --> 00:33:56,920
Your father-in-law

723
00:33:56,920 --> 00:33:59,359
knows how to buy vegetables

724
00:33:59,359 --> 00:34:00,519
and can cook now.

725
00:34:02,359 --> 00:34:03,119
Yes.

726
00:34:03,266 --> 00:34:05,155
But when your mother-in-law was alive,

727
00:34:05,440 --> 00:34:06,279
