735
00:34:21,920 --> 00:34:22,440
Here.

736
00:34:22,679 --> 00:34:23,840
Hurry, you worked hard.

737
00:34:23,840 --> 00:34:24,666
Give this to me.

738
00:34:24,688 --> 00:34:25,155
It's okay.

739
00:34:25,177 --> 00:34:25,755
Here.

740
00:34:25,840 --> 00:34:26,440
It's necessary.

741
00:34:27,000 --> 00:34:28,440
Take your time. Please come in.

742
00:34:29,559 --> 00:34:30,039
Lina.

743
00:34:30,440 --> 00:34:31,000
Come here.

744
00:34:31,000 --> 00:34:31,880
What are you doing?

745
00:34:32,159 --> 00:34:34,239
Look, Ms. Lian is back.

746
00:34:34,639 --> 00:34:36,679
They do this every day. I'm used to it.

747
00:34:39,760 --> 00:34:40,159
You...

748
00:34:42,960 --> 00:34:43,559
Look at me.

749
00:34:46,044 --> 00:34:47,190
You imitated her pretty well.

750
00:34:53,159 --> 00:34:54,000
I must say.

751
00:34:55,000 --> 00:34:56,719
She's gentle killer.

752
00:34:57,044 --> 00:34:58,320
She's over 50 years old, right?

753
00:34:58,599 --> 00:35:00,800
She had him wrapped around her fingers.

754
00:35:02,440 --> 00:35:03,840
Ms. Lian

755
00:35:05,079 --> 00:35:07,519
