What?

760
00:35:14,199 --> 00:35:16,239
You need to learn from her.
She's your role model.

761
00:35:18,880 --> 00:35:20,159
Here. Hurry up.

762
00:35:20,719 --> 00:35:21,960
Here.

763
00:35:23,355 --> 00:35:24,230
Please take a look.

764
00:35:24,800 --> 00:35:27,159
