765
00:35:27,555 --> 00:35:29,222
and served them all by myself.

766
00:35:30,239 --> 00:35:32,199
Let's not talk about the taste first.

767
00:35:32,960 --> 00:35:34,360
Isn't my intention commendable?

768
00:35:37,320 --> 00:35:39,154
I've always been the one
to rush home to cook.

769
00:35:39,155 --> 00:35:41,222
It's the first time
I've eaten ready-made food.

770
00:35:41,639 --> 00:35:42,280
Let me tell you.

771
00:35:42,519 --> 00:35:44,280
Those days are forever gone.

772
00:35:44,311 --> 00:35:46,711
You're finally getting your reward
after all the hardship.

773
00:35:47,679 --> 00:35:49,280
Come and take a seat.

774
00:35:49,679 --> 00:35:50,000
Here.

775
00:35:51,719 --> 00:35:52,199
Try it.

776
00:35:52,880 --> 00:35:53,280
Try it.

777
00:36:05,866 --> 00:36:06,800
I didn't expect it.

778
00:36:07,679 --> 00:36:08,199
This

779
00:36:09,644 --> 00:36:10,360
is the best dish

780
00:36:10,880 --> 00:36:11,519
I've ever eaten

