I didn't take good care of him.

804
00:37:16,020 --> 00:37:17,280
I thought he just caught a cold.

805
00:37:17,320 --> 00:37:18,355
It's not your fault.

806
00:37:20,800 --> 00:37:21,480
It's my fault.

807
00:37:22,719 --> 00:37:24,480
You were just hurrying back
to cook for me.

808
00:37:24,480 --> 00:37:25,770
